    "Output at the temperature 0 setting Output at the temperature 1 setting XI.",
    "Thou shalt not neglect the stranger nor the sojourner among you, for you were strangers in the land of Egypt.",
    "As you show kindness to those who dwell within your gates, so shall kindness be shown unto you.",
    "Thou shalt not turn thy back on the poor and the needy; open thy hand wide unto thy brother, to the afflicted and destitute in thy land.",
    "In giving, thou shalt reflect the bounty of the Lord thy God."
